{"tid":312193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麗港城現摺刀男　舖頭落閘避","createTime":"2017-07-07T08:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-07T13:28:26.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f635fd82a7f9766deee63956572b74a4999f67d","tid":312193,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:34:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20082008&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170707\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20082008%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170707&d=siqnVibP2mHqYsFzR%2FVzRmi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=65e048b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20082008%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170707&h=bd4ec551\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20082008&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170707</a><br />\n<br />\n麗港城現摺刀男　舖頭落閘避<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】觀塘麗港城昨日驚現持摺刀男子，警方派大批警員封鎖商場搜捕，但一直未有發現，由黃大仙警區重案組第一隊跟進。至晚上11時許，消息稱警方拘捕一名涉案男子，探員將他押往黃大仙下邨龍澤樓搜屋。<br />\n<br />\n案情指，昨午12時許，警方接報指黃大仙下邨龍悅樓外，有一名男子手持一把約6吋長的萬用刀，他其後進入港鐵黃大仙站登上一輛列車，並於藍田站落車。其後有市民報稱，看見持刀男走入麗港城商場後失去蹤影。警方接報大為緊張，派出至少10部警車及大批警員封鎖商場搜捕，但一直未有發現。疑人是年約40至50歲本地男子，身高約1.7米，?頭，肥身材，案發時身穿深色上衣，藍色牛仔褲，攜有黑色背包，戴黑手套。黃大仙警區重案組第一隊接手跟進，至昨晚拘捕涉案男子。"},{"pid":"30735101990a3debc87da3d64e965dd78a3e3371","tid":312193,"uid":38668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:43:31.000Z","msg":"邊個巴打黎"},{"pid":"6ef4921921a1a62b435a0d787a19a125db933330","tid":312193,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:44:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afb4e1474431ad1df3e0cde02dc7181af2122680","tid":312193,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T08:45:09.